⚙️ The 5-part Controlled Crossing Protocol

Think of this like your repeatable move:

1. Compress

Take one slice of your system.

Not:

“Pantheon solves everything”

But:

“This helps with one decision”

⸻

2. Bind to reality

Attach it to something real:
	•	a person
	•	a decision
	•	a problem
	•	a dataset

👉 No abstraction floating—must anchor

⸻

3. Act minimally

Do the smallest real action:
	•	give advice
	•	make a prediction
	•	build a tiny tool
	•	optimize something

⸻

4. Measure

You need feedback:
	•	did it save time?
	•	make money?
	•	improve outcome?

👉 no measurement = no crossing

⸻

5. Extract value

This is where you’ve been hesitating.

Keep it clean:
	•	small payment
	•	trade
	•	or clear proof

